creator: English First
descriptionHtml:
Track your child’s study progress with EF Parents App.

EF Parents is a product for parents of EF students aged 3-18 years old. It provides parents with their child’s learning experience and progress at EF Schools, such as:
- Covered in Class: See what your child learned in in every class session
- Child’s Practice: Track your child’s practice completion
- Progress: See assessment scores and feedback from teachers
- Media: See your child’s activity at EF school through photos and videos
- School News: Learn exciting information from our EF schools
- Staff Biography: Get to know EF staff and teachers
- Life Clubs: Engage in fun activities with EF Life Clubs

Learn more about EF: www.ef.co.id
Follow us on social media:
- Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ef.englishfirst
- Instagram: @ef_englishfirst
- Twitter: @ef_englishfirst
- YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/englishfirstID

Privacy Policy: http://www.ef.co.id/legal/privacy-policy
Terms and Conditions: http://www.ef.co.id/efp-tc
descriptionShort: Stay up to date with your child’s English language learning experience!

- Design: New improved design
